{"tid":82031,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲成日發啲好奇怪既夢？","createTime":"2017-01-15T16:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T03:53:09.000Z","uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3324e525062b49cdba1bf44ea199646a0133e224","tid":82031,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:42:46.000Z","msg":"一開始我係條街，跟住見到有人俾喪屍咬，<br />\n<br />\n我就好驚，靜靜咁潛入去自己屋企座大廈，<br />\n<br />\n好辛苦終於去到自己樓習，打開度防煙門，<br />\n<br />\n見到自己屋企好開心，即刻沖過去敲門啦，<br />\n<br />\n一路敲，一路驚，心諗點解咁撚耐仲唔開？<br />\n<br />\n之後就醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個夢成日都發，有時可能唔係喪屍而係其他怪物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e170d4b0e4e1d40046b4366c38f69d36e53f84f","tid":82031,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68dc4e2575f36b8697f8b502b22afb731db82d2e","tid":82031,"uid":51388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"咪睇咁多科幻片啦<br />\n利申 試過發夢被哥斯拉追同做Mission Impossible"},{"pid":"1eb3a4807b52bd6b092d1876312fc69ba9000a84","tid":82031,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪睇咁多科幻片啦<br />\n利申 試過發夢被哥斯拉追同做Mission Impossible</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然好鍾意睇科幻片 但係已經好耐冇睇<br />\n最後嗰套已經係屍殺列車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775753f54edf59143a6b45e41eb3f8f3641cab74","tid":82031,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T17:05:01.000Z","msg":"有 曾經發夢同洛克人傾計 傾乜就唔知  印象中個畫面係我同佢面對面口郁郁 講緊野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93070dd63c3ac3ef6d83d125648b9ec4df9943c3","tid":82031,"uid":51890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T17:06:00.000Z","msg":"我成日都發俾喪屍追嘅夢，都真心幾驚下<i